The motion of the quadrotor may be predicted by integrating the forward dynamics equations we have derived where the wrenches on the airframe (T𝛕)=(−b−b−b−b0−db0dbdb0−db0k−kk−k)(ϖ12ϖ22ϖ32ϖ42)=𝐀(ϖ12ϖ22ϖ32ϖ42)
